A '''thief''' is a commonly found [[monster]] in [[RuneScape Classic]]. Though they are rarely trained on, some players kill them for their herb drops.

The [[blanket]] thieves in the [[Ardougne sewers]] are encountered during the [[Monk's Friend]] [[quest]].
==Locations==
*[[Ardougne sewers]]
*South-East [[Varrock]]
*[[Port Sarim]]

